  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  itemTitle: "Transmisyon Ya\u011F Bas\u0131n\xE7 G\xF6stergesi"
  itemDescription: "28 VAC ile \xE7al\u0131\u015F\u0131r\nTransmitterdan ald\u0131\u011F\u0131
    bilgi ile bas\u0131nc\u0131 psi cinsinden s\xFCrekli g\xF6sterir.\n30 psi minimum,
    40-60 psi devaml\u0131, 70 psi maksimum olmal\u0131d\u0131r.\nTransmisyon ya\u011F
    bas\u0131n\xE7 transmitter\u0131, transmisyon \xFCst kab\u0131 sa\u011F taraf\u0131nda
    ya\u011F manifoldunun \xFCzerindedir. Bas\u0131n\xE7 de\u011Ferini voltaj sinyalleri
    ile g\xF6stergeye iletir."
  isListText: 1
