--- !u!114 &118231702
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 118231699}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 4cc07b05bfbfa49cd8a511b7a3233be5, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  itemTitle: Dual Takometre(RPM Saati)
  itemDescription: "Ana rotor ve motor \xE7\u0131k\u0131\u015F \u015Faft\u0131 devrini
    g\xF6sterir.(Motor 6600 Rotor 324 RPM) Her iki g\xF6sterge takometre jenerat\xF6r\xFCn\xFC
    ay\u0131ran elektrik ba\u011Flant\u0131l\u0131 e\u015Fzamanl\u0131 motora sahiptir.\nRotor
    ibresi i\xE7 skalay\u0131, motor ibresi d\u0131\u015F skalay\u0131 g\xF6sterir.\nG\xFC\xE7
    t\xFCrbini (N2) Takometre jenerat\xF6r\xFC, motorun sol \xFCst taraf\u0131nda
    N2 di\u015Fli kutusu \xFCzerindedir,dual takometreye irtibatl\u0131d\u0131r.\nRotor
    takometre jenerat\xF6r\xFC, transmisyon sa\u011F alt taraf\u0131nda hidrolik
    pompa ile beraber drive quill \xFCzerindedir,dual takometreye irtibatl\u0131d\u0131r.\nN1
    Takometre(Gas Producer)G\xF6stergesi\nMotor gaz \xFCretici t\xFCrbin(N1) devrini
    y\xFCzde olarak g\xF6sterir.N1 di\u015Fli kutusundaki N1 takometre jenerat\xF6r\xFCne
    ba\u011Fl\u0131d\u0131r.(101.5 max.)\nN1 takometre jenerat\xF6r\xFC motorun sa\u011F
    taraf\u0131nda, N1 di\u015Fli kutusu \xFCzerindedir. N1 t\xFCrbin devri sinyallerini
    g\xF6stergeye iletir."
  isListText: 1
