  itemTitle: "N1 Takometre(Gas Producer)G\xF6stergesi"
  itemDescription: "Motor gaz \xFCretici t\xFCrbin(N1) devrini y\xFCzde olarak g\xF6sterir.
    N1 di\u015Fli kutusundaki N1 takometre jenerat\xF6r\xFCne ba\u011Fl\u0131d\u0131r.
    (101.5 max.)\nN1 takometre jenerat\xF6r\xFC motorun sa\u011F taraf\u0131nda,
    N1 di\u015Fli kutusu \xFCzerindedir. N1 t\xFCrbin devri sinyallerini g\xF6stergeye
    iletir."
