  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  itemTitle: "S\xFCrat Saati (Airspeed Indicator)"
  itemDescription: "G\xF6sterge panelinde 2 adettir.\nStandart pitot statik g\xF6stergesidir.
    \nStatik porttan atmosfer bas\u0131nc\u0131 ile pitot t\xFCp\xFCnden ge\xE7en
    toplam hava bas\u0131nc\u0131 aras\u0131ndaki fark\u0131 (Dinamik Bas\u0131n\xE7)
    \xF6l\xE7erek hava h\u0131z\u0131n\u0131 knot cinsinden g\xF6sterir. \nPitot
    t\xFCp\xFC burunda olan modellerde 112 knot\nPitot t\xFCp\xFC \xFCstte olan modellerde
    124 knot maksimum de\u011Fer belirtir."
  isListText: 1
