  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  itemTitle: "DC Y\xFCkmetre"
  itemDescription: "Ana ve standby jenerat\xF6rleri i\xE7in birer adettir. \n\xC7\u0131k\u0131\u015F
    veya toplam kapasitelerinin y\xFCzdesi olarak y\xFCk\xFC g\xF6sterir.\nShuntler
    vas\u0131tas\u0131 ile y\xFCkmetreler \xE7al\u0131\u015F\u0131r.\nStandby shunt
