--- !u!114 &1664357546
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 1664357543}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 4cc07b05bfbfa49cd8a511b7a3233be5, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  itemTitle: "Suni Ufuk Sistemi ve G\xF6stergeleri (Attitude Indicators)"
  itemDescription: "Pilot ve copilot suni ufuk q\xF6stergeleri ile pitch ve roll
    gyrolar\u0131ndan olu\u015Fur.\nSistem 115 VAC bustan enerjilenir ve g\xF6stergeler
    1 amperlik sigortalar ile korunurlar.\nHelikopter, gyrolar\u0131n zarar g\xF6rmemesi
    i\xE7in, g\xFCc\xFC kapat\u0131ld\u0131ktan 25 dakika sonra \xE7ekilmelidir.
    Bu s\xFCre dolmadan \xE7ekmek zorunda kal\u0131n\u0131rsa tekrar sisteme g\xFC\xE7
    verilir. \nPilot ve copilot suni ufuk g\xF6stergeleri panele montelidir. Helikopterin
    ufka g\xF6re durumunu g\xF6sterir. Dal\u0131\u015F t\u0131rman\u0131\u015F\u0131
    (pitch), k\xFCre hareketinin u\xE7ak minyat\xFCr\xFCne olan durumu ile; yat\u0131\u015F\u0131
    (roll) g\xF6stergenin \xFCst k\u0131sm\u0131ndaki ibre ve skala ile g\xF6sterir.
    Her iki eksen, ayar d\xFC\u011Fmeleri ile s\u0131f\u0131rlanabilir. \nCopilot
    g\xF6stergesi PULL TO CAGE koluna sahiptir, gyroyu tutar ve serbest b\u0131rak\u0131r.
    \u0130nverter ON konumuna al\u0131nmadan \xF6nce  yap\u0131lmal\u0131d\u0131r.\nG\xF6stergenin
    i\xE7erisinde g\xF6r\xFCnmeyen OFF bayra\u011F\u0131 vard\u0131r, g\xF6sterge
    g\xFCc\xFCnde kesilme olursa hata vererek g\xF6r\xFCn\xFCr hale gelir."
  isListText: 1
